<concept id="id_3" class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">Record</title><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li ">
                <p class="- topic/p ">From the main toolbar, click on <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Web Recorder Utility</b> icon to open the Web Recorder.</p>
                <p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/recording-webui-test/web-record-icon.png" scope="external" width="200" class="- topic/image "/></p>
            </li><li class="- topic/li ">
                <p class="- topic/p ">In the displayed <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Web Recorder</b>:</p>
                <ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li ">Enter URL: <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">https://demo-store.katalon.com</codeph>.</li><li class="- topic/li ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Select a browser to start recording (Chrome is recommended).</p>
                        <p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/recording-webui-test/selectb-browser.png" scope="external" width="750" class="- topic/image "/></p>
                    </li></ul>
            </li><li class="- topic/li ">
                <p class="- topic/p ">Wait until the browser is launched and ready to interact.</p>
                <p class="- topic/p ">When you hover an element, the browser highlights and displays that element's correspondent XPath on the top of the page.</p>
                <p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/recording-webui-test/xpath.png" scope="external" class="- topic/image "/></p>
                <note type="tip" class="- topic/note ">
                    <ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li ">
                            <p class="- topic/p ">You can use hotkey to capture objects (pressing the combination of &lt;Command + back quote&gt;). The captured object will be highlighted with a green border.</p>
                        </li></ul>
                </note>
            </li><li class="- topic/li ">
                <p class="- topic/p ">Interact with the web page. In this scenario, we will sign in and purchase a tank top.</p>
                <p class="- topic/p ">During your recording, <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Katalon Web Recorder</b> captures all the objects that you have interacted with. When you enter the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Password</b> field, <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Katalon Web Recorder</b> uses the '<xref href="../../../../Create_tests/Keywords/Keywords_Description_In_Katalon_Studio/Web-UI-Keywords/webui-set-encrypted-text/webui-set-encrypted-text.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Set Encrypted Text</xref>' keyword automatically. This input value will be encrypted to ensure security.</p>
                <p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/recording-webui-test/recorded-actions.png" scope="external" width="750" class="- topic/image "/></p>
            </li><li class="- topic/li ">
                <p class="- topic/p ">Once you finish purchasing &gt; click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Save script</b> to stop recording and save the captured objects. <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Katalon Web Recorder</b> exports a list of objects used in the test case.</p>
                <p class="- topic/p ">Create a new folder or select an existing one in <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Object Repository</b> &gt; click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">OK</b>.</p>
                <p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/recording-webui-test/select-repo.png" scope="external" width="750" class="- topic/image "/></p>
                <note type="note" class="- topic/note ">
                    <ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/> allows you to continue recording using the existing test case to reduce your effort on modifying existing ones. <image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/recording-webui-test/test-case-modifying.png" scope="external" width="750" class="- topic/image "/>
                        </li></ul>
                </note>
            </li></ol></conbody></concept>